                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8931" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0977</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">790 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">逐浪前行——爱波瑞的战略创业之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Riding the waves-Abrain&#39;s strategic entrepreneurial road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高辉，谷文松，张建宇，高楠，张然</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津爱波瑞科技发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略创业；企业家精神；资源编排；精益咨询；爱波瑞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strategic entrepreneurship; Entrepreneurship; Resource orchestration; Lean consulting; Abrain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略创业是企业应对不确定性环境，实现持续成长的重要工具。本案例详细展示了民营咨询企业爱波瑞从ISO9000认证到精益咨询、从精益咨询到制造业论坛和实训中心，再到数字化产品的三次战略创业过程。基于战略创业、资源编排和企业家精神等理论知识，案例具体说明了企业家王洪艳如何在企业家精神的驱动下，综合考虑外部环境与资源和能力的动态变化，灵活调整战略决策和创业方向，通过恰当的资源编排方式，在机会探索与优势开发之间寻求平衡，进而不断实现企业目标的过程机制。本案例旨在帮助学生深入理解战略创业的微观过程与内在机理，同时也为其他咨询企业应对不确定性环境谋求转型发展提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Strategic entrepreneurship is an important tool for companies to cope with uncertain environment and realize sustainable growth. The case demonstrates in detail the three strategic entrepreneurship processes of private consulting firm Abrain from ISO9000 certification to lean consulting, from lean consulting to manufacturing forum and training center, and then to digital products. Based on the strategic entrepreneurship, resource orchestration and entrepreneurship theories, the case specifies how entrepreneur Wang Hongyan, driven by entrepreneurship, takes into account the dynamic changes of the external environment and resources and capabilities, flexibly adjusts the strategic decision and entrepreneurial direction, and seeks for a balance between exploring the opportunities and exploiting the advantages by means of appropriate resource orchestration so as to continuously realize the process mechanism of the enterprise&#39;s goals. This case aims to help students understand the micro-process and internal mechanism of strategic entrepreneurship, and also provide reference for other consulting firms to deal with the uncertainty of the environment and seek transformation and development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略创业；战略转型；企业家精神；资源编排</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
